prompt_text: Describe the smartphone application that you use the most.
content_text: The application in my phone that I use the most is probably YouTube because it helps me learn a lot about new things and it helps me overcome obstacles that I face in my daily life. Of. I can use YouTube to learn a lot of new things and also if I face any issues with my life, I can use YouTube to overcome that. If I face any issues with any electric appliances or if I face any issue going into a new field, I can learn a lot about that from YouTube. And YouTube is also a nice app to use on your free time.
